{"ja466:0.1":"Jataka ","ja466:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","ja466:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja466:0.4":"3. Samuddavanijajataka ","ja466:1.1":"“Kasanti vapanti te jana, ","ja466:1.2":"Manuja kammaphalupajivino; ","ja466:1.3":"Nayimassa dipakassa bhagino, ","ja466:1.4":"Jambudipa idameva no varam”. ","ja466:2.1":"“Tipancarattupagatamhi cande, ","ja466:2.2":"Vego maha hehiti sagarassa; ","ja466:2.3":"Uplavissam dipamimam ularam, ","ja466:2.4":"Ma vo vadhi gacchatha lenamannam”. ","ja466:3.1":"“Na jatuyam sagaravarivego, ","ja466:3.2":"Uplavissam dipamimam ularam; ","ja466:3.3":"Tam me nimittehi bahuhi dittham, ","ja466:3.4":"Ma bhetha kim socatha modathavho. ","ja466:4.1":"Pahutabhakkham bahuannapanam, ","ja466:4.2":"Pattattha avasamimam ularam; ","ja466:4.3":"Na vo bhayam patipassami kinci, ","ja466:4.4":"Aputtaputtehi pamodathavho”. ","ja466:5.1":"“Yo devoyam dakkhinayam disayam, ","ja466:5.2":"Khemanti pakkosati tassa saccam; ","ja466:5.3":"Na uttaro vedi bhayabhayassa, ","ja466:5.4":"Ma bhetha kim socatha modathavho”. ","ja466:6.1":"“Yatha ime vippavadanti yakkha, ","ja466:6.2":"Eko bhayam samsati khemameko; ","ja466:6.3":"Tadingha mayham vacanam sunatha, ","ja466:6.4":"Khippam lahum ma vinassimha sabbe. ","ja466:7.1":"Sabbe samagamma karoma navam, ","ja466:7.2":"Donim dalham sabbayantupapannam; ","ja466:7.3":"Sace ayam dakkhino saccamaha, ","ja466:7.4":"Mogham patikkosati uttaroyam; ","ja466:7.5":"Sa ceva no hehiti apadattha, ","ja466:7.6":"Imanca dipam na pariccajema. ","ja466:8.1":"Sace ca kho uttaro saccamaha, ","ja466:8.2":"Mogham patikkosati dakkhinoyam; ","ja466:8.3":"Tameva navam abhiruyha sabbe, ","ja466:8.4":"Evam mayam sotthi taremu param. ","ja466:9.1":"Na ve suganham pathamena settham, ","ja466:9.2":"Kanitthamapathagatam gahetva; ","ja466:9.3":"Yo cidha taccham paviceyya ganhati, ","ja466:9.4":"Sa ve naro setthamupeti thanam. ","ja466:10.1":"Yathapi te sagaravarimajjhe, ","ja466:10.2":"Sakammuna sotthi vahimsu vanija; ","ja466:10.3":"Anagatattham pativijjhiyana, ","ja466:10.4":"Appampi nacceti sa bhuripanno. ","ja466:11.1":"Bala ca mohena rasanugiddha, ","ja466:11.2":"Anagatam appativijjhiyattham; ","ja466:11.3":"Paccuppanne sidanti atthajate, ","ja466:11.4":"Samuddamajjhe yatha te manussa. ","ja466:12.1":"Anagatam patikayiratha kiccam, ","ja466:12.2":"‘Ma mam kiccam kiccakale byadhesi’; ","ja466:12.3":"Tam tadisam patikatakiccakarim, ","ja466:12.4":"Na tam kiccam kiccakale byadheti”ti. ","ja466:13.1":"Samuddavanijajatakam tatiyam. "}